name: Kendu Inu (KENDU)
description: Uniting the six native Japanese dog breeds. Kendu is the keeper of peace, the preserver of life, and the protector of unity. Join the pack! The mantra of the Kendu community is "We do not gamble, we work." In Kendu's meme ecosystem, you will find a decentralized community of countless talented, passionate, and driven individuals from all walks of life, working together and alone with the common goal of achieving Kendu's brand recognition and success on the world stage.
